{
  "text": "14 Among proximal BA aneurysms, fenestration of the BA has been seen in 35.5% to 50% of cases. [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] It has been postulated that alteration of flow and hemodynamics seen with this anatomic variant, in combination with morphological changes seen in the medial walls of the fenestration, predispose BA fenestration anatomy to aneurysm formation.",
